de.schenk.jrtrace.annotations

Annotation Type XThis


  • @Retention(value=CLASS)
@Target(value=PARAMETER)
public @interface XThis
    If a parameter of the injected method is annotated with XThis the object of the target method will be injected into this parameter when called. It is in the responsibility of the developer to ensure that the types of the target object and the type of the method parameter match.
    Author:
    Christian Schenk
